Class EvaluationFunction_Random

  • java.lang.Object
    • tree.node.evaluator.EvaluationFunction_Random
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEvaluationFunction

    public class EvaluationFunction_Random
extends Object
implements IEvaluationFunction
    This evaluation function returns a random value regardless of the given node. This is rarely a good idea, but is ok for testing stuff.
